We are able to seize land form large estate, mostly uncultivated land and hand them out to peasants and veteran-run cooperatives, reducing unemployment.

[? if ldr_promise_failed : Unfortunately, our land seizure has led us to enter a deficit, breaking our agreement with the Liberals, and their representatives have already requested a meeting with us. ?]

